    If instead the intended API were “pass the final valid index”, then the     
    call would need to be:                                                      
                                                                                
                                                                                
     crc8(buf, sizeof(buf) - 1);                                                
                                                                                
                                                                                
    But that would be a poor design here because the parameter is named len,    
    and callers normally expect length parameters to be counts. The better fix  
    is to keep the caller unchanged and fix the loop condition.                 
                                                                                
